msgstr "manged"

#: ../../M/manged.rst:7
msgid "/mahnjd/, n\\."
msgstr "/mahnjd/, 名詞"

#: ../../M/manged.rst:9
msgid ""
"[probably from the French ‘manger’ or Italian ‘mangiare’, to eat; perhaps "
"influenced by English ‘mange’, ‘mangy’] adj. Refers to anything that is "
"mangled or damaged, usually beyond repair. \"The disk was manged after the "
"electrical storm.\" Compare :ref:`mung`\\."
msgstr ""
"[おそらくフランス語の‘manger’あるいはイタリア語の‘mangiare’、食べる、から。おそらく英語の‘mange’、‘mangy’の影響を受けている]形容詞"
" ずたずたにされた、あるいは損傷した、たいてい修復不能なまでに、あらゆるものを指す。「ディスクは雷雨のあとmangedになった」。\\ "
":ref:`mung`\\ と比較せよ。"
